    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = v1
    v2 = (wp.cos(wp.abs(tmp + 0.79)) + (wp.cos(v0 + 0.59) - 0.22))
    v1 = v1
    tmp = (wp.cos((v1 + 0.22 + v0 + 0.70)) - 0.81)
    v1 = 0.34
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.abs((v2 + 0.51 * v0 + 0.16)))
    v2 = v0
